 tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 15, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cny1665702550298.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cny1665702550298.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cny1665702550298.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cny1665702550298\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Code Container\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Code Container is a type of <dfn class=\"term\">Property</dfn> that holds code, such as\n    ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers,\n    operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cny1665702550298__section_d1q_pd5_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d253968e54\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uqv1665702561461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uqv1665702561461.html\" title=\"An Entity is an abstract data type that defines a logical data aggregation and its associated default characteristics and behavior. It may be mapped to a table in a DBMS, and is most frequently used to represent the application data, but it can also represent transient data, a collection of controls, or constant data.\">Entity</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lym1665702585074.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lym1665702585074.html\" title=\"A Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in an Entity. This could represent a column in a DBMS table or data that is not stored in the database, such as a derived field or a user interface control. Its associated properties define the way it is stored, its GUI representation, and default behavior.\">Field</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifc1665702608950.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifc1665702608950.html\" title=\"A Component is a Main Development Object that defines an executable part of an application. It defines the data structure used to access data, the layout (if applicable) used to present it, and the actions used to modify, validate, and store data.\">Component</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"quf1665702550125.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/quf1665702550125.html\" title=\"An Application Shell is a Main Development Object that defines the main executable component of an application (Windows or character-based) or application server.\">Application Shell</a>, and their\n                  specializations</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Trigger, Operation, Function, Entry, Layout</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cny1665702550298__table_d10451e1_d10452e1_d10453e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cny1665702550298__section_x2t_xd5_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d253968e228\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cny1665702550298__p_d94526e1_d94527e1_d94528e1\">Code Container specializes <dfn class=\"term\">Property</dfn> in the\n        following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"cny1665702550298__ul_ppp_yd5_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cny1665702550298__li_d36794e1_d36795e1_d36796e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cny1665702550298__p_d94529e1_d94530e1_d94531e1\">It can only contain script of some kind</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cny1665702550298__li_d36797e1_d36798e1_d36799e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cny1665702550298__p_d94532e1_d94533e1_d94534e1\">It has a dedicated editor, which supports syntax\n            highlighting</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612415\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612415\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Code Container Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 15, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Code Container A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout. Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: — Main Development Object? No Part of: Entity , Field , Component , Application Shell , and their specializations Contains: Trigger, Operation, Function, Entry, Layout Generalization: Property Specializations — Compilation Output — Specialization Code Container specializes Property in the following ways: It can only contain script of some kind It has a dedicated editor, which supports syntax highlighting Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}